I"ÿ<p>Counting the number of offenses for each ori in each month and recording the results:</p>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>bysort year month ori: egen crimes = count(offense)
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Counting how many unique oris there are:</p>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>by ori, sort: gen nvals = _n == 1 
count if nvals
drop nvals
</code></pre></div></div>
